        settingsTip: 'Open game settings',
        rulesTitle: '📖 How to play',
        closedBtn: 'CLOSE',
        understoodBtn: 'GOT IT, LET\'S PLAY!',
        rulesContent: `<div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">📡</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">1. Connect a channel</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Enter a Twitch channel username. The game collects messages in real time.</div></div></div><div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">🙈</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">2. Hide the chat!</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Close the chat — guess by writing style, not by peeking.</div></div></div><div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">🎭</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">3. 12 modes</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Classic, true/fake, missing word, two of four, 7TV, emoji chain and more.</div></div></div><div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">📣</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">4. Mods</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Type <b style="color:var(--c-accent2);">!s text</b> — message pops up on the left. Raids, subs and bits too.</div></div></div><div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">🔥</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">5. Streak &amp; bonuses</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Consecutive correct answers = score multiplier. Hints ½, skip, highlight — one each per game.</div></div></div>`,
        faqContent: `<div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">🔌</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">Can't connect to chat</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Check the username. 7TV requires https.</div></div></div><div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">👥</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">How many viewers are needed?</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Minimum 4 for an early start. Target is the slider in settings.</div></div></div><div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">🔗</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">What is "Links only"?</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Only messages with links participate. Emote modes are disabled.</div></div></div><div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">🔗</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">What is "Emoji chain"?</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">One emoji is kept from a real message and words are replaced with ⬜. Guess the author by emoji placement style.</div></div></div><div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">🔢</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">How many rounds will there be?</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Exactly as many as players who joined the round. 17 of 20 joined — 17 questions. Each message is unique and each joined player participates exactly once — no repeats.</div></div></div><div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">🎲</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">How often do modes appear?</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Each round the mode is chosen <b>equally at random</b> from available ones. With N active modes roughly <b>100% ÷ N</b> each.</div></div></div><div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">💾</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">Is data saved?</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Settings and last 20 games are in localStorage. Nothing is sent anywhere.</div></div></div><div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">✨</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">Authors</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Idea by: afaplein (aka cyberr) &amp; <a href="https://www.twitch.tv/lootych" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--c-accent);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">Lootych</a>. Built by <a href="https://t.me/rudionee" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--c-accent);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">Rudionee</a>.</div></div></div>`,
