        rfRulesContent: `<div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">✏️</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">1. Set the keyword</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">In settings (⚙️) enter the word chat uses to join — e.g. <b style="color:var(--c-green);">join</b> or any word you like. Or enable "Any message = entry".</div></div></div><div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">▶️</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">2. Open the raffle</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Click <b style="color:var(--c-accent);">Open raffle</b> — chat can now join. The status dot turns green. Close the raffle when you have enough entries.</div></div></div><div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">💬</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">3. Chat types the keyword</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Both <b style="color:var(--c-green);">!word</b> and plain <b style="color:var(--c-green);">word</b> count, case-insensitive. Each entrant gets their tickets and lands in the list.</div></div></div><div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">🎰</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">4. Spin the wheel</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Click <b style="color:var(--c-gold);">SPIN THE WHEEL</b>. The animation picks a winner — CS-style roulette, elimination, or instant (set in ⚙️).</div></div></div><div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">🏆</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">5. Winner chosen!</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Ask the winner to type something — their message appears under the card. Account age and follow status are shown. Reroll if they don't respond.</div></div></div><div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">⚙️</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">Bonuses & settings</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Give <b>bonus tickets</b> to subs, VIPs, mods, and first-timers. Enable follow check — a reroll hint appears if the winner isn't a follower. Entry list and history survive F5.</div></div></div><div class="rule-row"><div class="rule-ico">📢</div><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:2px;">!say command for mods</div><div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--c-muted);line-height:1.55;">Moderators and the streamer can type <b style="color:var(--c-accent2);">!say text</b> in chat — the message appears in the bottom-left banner on screen. Works in all modes.</div></div></div>`,
